info.description:
DSON - Doge Serialized Object Notation
======================================

Scott Torborg - storborg@gmail.com

The ``dson`` module is a drop-in replacement for ``json``, but encodes and decodes to DSON (Doge Serialized Object Notation).

For more details about DSON see the `DSON specification <http://dogeon.org>`.


Installation
============

Install with pip::

    $ pip install dson
info.keywords: doge serialized object notation json encoder decoder
